
  Froslass    Ice Type Pokémon

  It freezes foes with an icy 
  breath nearly -60 degrees F. 
   What seems to be its body is 
  actually hollow. 
	Evolution Chain
      Snorunt ► Glalie

Stage 2 Forms:
  glalie
  froslass

